{"Id":830354,"Title":"兰陵王 题唐写金光明最胜王经坚牢地神品第十八卷子","Dynasty":"近现代","Author":"赵熙","Context":"李唐笔。千岁香严手迹。何人考、年月姓名，惟有坚牢字千百。宣南四立壁。收得。禅心一箧。是杨云、宣统二年，手割敦煌万山色。秋风满京国。叹谏草无功，天黯南北。伤心马角乌头白。便水远山远，一声去也，燕云如梦万里隔。剩身外经册。荣德。故山碧。准白发头陀，身傍诸佛。梵天花雨峨眉宅。只甚日携手，卷中词客。金光明字，月一片，照净室。","PoertyType":null,"Cipai":"兰陵王","Status":2,"Rank":0,"Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"First":null,"Guid":"a50d29543172fba8bf06e3c0456aa685","Step":0,"Verses":[{"Id":5103484,"Sentence":"李唐笔。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"li táng bi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":0,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103485,"Sentence":"千岁香严手迹。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qiān suì xiāng yán shǒu jì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":1,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103487,"Sentence":"宣南四立壁。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"xuān nā sì lì bì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":3,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103488,"Sentence":"收得。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shōu dé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":4,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103489,"Sentence":"禅心一箧。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"chán xīn yī qiè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":5,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103491,"Sentence":"秋风满京国。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"qīu fēng mǎn jīng guó ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":7,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103495,"Sentence":"剩身外经册。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"shèng shēn wài jīng cè ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":11,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103496,"Sentence":"荣德。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"róng dé ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":12,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103497,"Sentence":"故山碧。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"gù shān bì ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"English":null,"Sort":13,"Dynasty":"近现代"},{"Id":5103486,"Sentence":"何人考、年月姓名，惟有坚牢字千百。","Rank":0,"PoetryId":null,"Pinyin":"hé rén kǎo 、nián yuè xìng mǐng ，wéi yǒu jiān láo zì qiān bǎi ","Tag":null,"Explanation":null,"Englis